[[!meta title="MIT SIPB MySQL Service"]]
[**sql.mit.edu**](http://sql.mit.edu/)

This service provides [MySQL](http://dev.mysql.com/doc) databases to
[MIT certificate](http://ca.mit.edu/) holders. SQL commands can be
issued from any host, client, and/or script of your choice; simply
connect to the MySQL server at [**sql.mit.edu**](http://sql.mit.edu/)
using your MySQL username and password.

To sign up and create databases, visit
[**sql.mit.edu**](http://sql.mit.edu/). For information about using the
service with a group locker, see [the FAQ](/faq/27).
